    "title": "Hiring Medical Officer at Granules India",
    "description": "Granules India, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Medical Officer for our Pimpri-Chinchwad operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Granules India:\nGranules India is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct routine health assessments and screenings\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n• Coordinate with multidisciplinary teams for comprehensive patient management\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n• Ensure patient privacy and maintain confidentiality\n• Respond to medical emergencies and provide immediate care\n• Maintain sterile environments and follow infection control protocols\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Medical Terminology\n• Proficiency in BLS/ACLS\n• Proficiency in Medical Ethics\n• Proficiency in ICU Management\n• Proficiency in ICD-10\n• Proficiency in Telemedicine\n• Proficiency in Medical Coding\n• Proficiency in HIPAA Compliance\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pimpri-Chinchwad, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Granules India!",
